Bengals Beat Bills 23-20, Sending Buffalo to First Loss of NFL Season

-- B y   E r i k   M a t u s z e w s k i
-- 
2011-10-02T20:18:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-02/bengals-beat-bills-23-20-sending-buffalo-to-first-loss-of-nfl-season.html
The  Cincinnati Bengals  beat Buffalo
23-20 on a 43-yard field goal by Mike Nugent as time expired to
send the Bills to their first loss of the season.  The Bengals rallied from a 14-point halftime deficit at
Paul Brown Stadium in Cincinnati,  Ohio , to improve to 2-2 and
drop the Bills to 3-1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Erik Matuszewski at 
 matuszewski@bloomberg.net  